Scripts.Name: Works with other power-ups
Scripts.Description: The version compatible with other power-ups. Read main description for more info.

Description:
Lets you place the Boo Mario power-up in your levels. Model ID: 254, Behavior: 0x13003CE4. Replaces big snowman bottom behavior. Model ID 255 is also used for this tweak.
Select the "Auto import" option to be able to place this in any level (Extends bank 03).
Select the "Works with other power-ups" option if you want to use multiple GomePlayTV power-ups in a single ROM (But to get the models in with this option, you must import both yourself after downloading them from http://www.mediafire.com/file/bzjuq0g3l4h9li1/GPTV_Boo_Mario.zip/file, and following the instructions in the readme.)
